[
{Momoe Nagisa was originally a magical girl who signed a contract with Kyubey. The reason for becoming a magical girl was so that her dying mother could eat cheese cake. Later, she regretted not directly rescuing her mother as she had made her wish. After transforming into a witch, she became Charlotte, the confection witch. In the world without witches created by Madoka Kaname after becoming a god, she was redeemed by the "Principle of the Ring" before becoming a witch. She accepted the witch "in order to eat cheese again" like Miki Sayaka. She embarked on a mission to break away from the cause and effect of the world and became the messenger of the "Principle of the Circle".}
]

      [
      {The snack witch. The nature is greed. If you want to monopolize everything, you will never give up. It can make all kinds of snacks infinitely, but it can never make its favorite cheese. There are two forms.
1: Ragdoll-like initial state, expressionless.
2: A big worm comes out of the mouth of the first form. It has a body with red polka dots on a black background, and one red and one blue wing on each side of its head (useless).}
