[
{Nagisa's fighting method is rather special. Instead of summoning weapons to attack, she summons various familiars (the familiars of all witches in the old world) to fight through an infinite cycle of "face-changing". In addition, she can also use her own weapon, the trumpet-shaped bubble machine, to blow out some bubbles to hinder enemies or attack.}
