[
{When she first appeared, she was discovered by Madoka Kaname and Sayaka Miki in the form of an unhatched witch's egg ("Seed of Lament"). After hatching, he became the confection witch Charlotte, and fought against Mami Tomoe brought by Madoka in the barrier. After being restrained by Tomoe Mami in her initial form, she transformed a second time and bit off Tomoe Mami's head and devoured it, and was later eliminated by Akemi Homura who arrived.}
